Proposed classes for our Mastermind program:
Director()
Arbiter()
Console()
AsciiArt()
Player()
Code()

Director() - Responsible for controlling the flow of gameplay
Arbiter() - Responsible for taking player's guess, checking aginst the code, returning hint
Console() - Responsible for taking input and displaying output
AsciiArt() - Responsible for displaying ASCII art and user-friendly messages.
Player() - Keep track of the player's identity, and guesses
Code() - To generate and store a four digit integer code (between 1000 and 9999)